metadata.description:
Your Dog Zone NFT acts as your "Freedom Fighter's Club" membership card, granting access to members-only benefits. That includes access to our algorithmic trading platform, where the revenue earned will be shared among holders. In addition, the community will be able to unlock more perks through roadmap activation. 
Holders of Dog Zone traps that have both male and female traits will be able to breed the dogs and be rewarded with new unique NFT puppies.
metadata.name: DOG ZONE #1
